data.description: BRAND NEW PLY GEM SIMONTON WINDOWS AND PATIO DOOR  installed 2/2/24! New roof from 2016. Water heater updated in 2023. Master bathroom was remodeled in 2020. Seller has quote to refinish hardwood floors. Seller will provide credit to quote given. Desirable two-story home in peaceful Wildwood neighborhood! Four bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms, freshly painted, fresh carpets, and plenty of natural light throughout! Kitchen features granite countertops, convenient island, stainless steel appliances, and an eat-in area. The family room hosts a lovely gas log fireplace and provides a wonderful view to your large fenced-in backyard and patio! The master bedroom boasts an en-suite bathroom. Just minutes away from a plethora of dining and shopping options! Don't miss out on this opportunity!
